{
  "page": "House Sunglass",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Sunglass of Sweetport Sound</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Sunglass.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Sunglass.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f4/House_Sunglass.svg/250px-House_Sunglass.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f4/House_Sunglass.svg/375px-House_Sunglass.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f4/House_Sunglass.svg/500px-House_Sunglass.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Coat of arms</th><td>\nSeven golden seven-pointed stars in a ring on white<br /><i>(Argent, seven mullets of seven points or)</i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Seat</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Sweetport_Sound\" title=\"Sweetport Sound\">Sweetport Sound</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Sunglass\" title=\"Lord Sunglass\">Sunglass</a> (in <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Blackwater_Bay\" title=\"Blackwater Bay\">Blackwater Bay</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Sweetport_Sound\" title=\"Lord of Sweetport Sound\">Lord of Sweetport Sound</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Overlord</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_Dragonstone\" title=\"House Baratheon of Dragonstone\">House Baratheon of Dragonstone</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Sunglass of Sweetport Sound</b> is a noble house sworn to <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>. The location of <a href=\"/index.php/Sweetport_Sound\" title=\"Sweetport Sound\">Sweetport Sound</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">crownlands</a> has not been stated.\n</p><p>Their blazon is composed by seven golden seven-pointed stars in a ring on white.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Their motto does not appear in the books.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#House_Sunglass_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Sunglass at the end of the third century</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Household\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Household</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Sunglass&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Sunglass&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Targaryen_Loyalist_Kip_Ayers.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c0/House_Targaryen_Loyalist_Kip_Ayers.JPG/300px-House_Targaryen_Loyalist_Kip_Ayers.JPG\" width=\"300\" height=\"192\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c0/House_Targaryen_Loyalist_Kip_Ayers.JPG/450px-House_Targaryen_Loyalist_Kip_Ayers.JPG 1.5x, /images/c/c0/House_Targaryen_Loyalist_Kip_Ayers.JPG 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Targaryen_Loyalist_Kip_Ayers.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a> loyalist displaying the arms of House Sunglass, by Kip Ayers © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Guncer_Sunglass\" title=\"Guncer Sunglass\">Guncer Sunglass</a> answers the summons of <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a> when he calls his banners against King <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey I Baratheon</a>. Guncer is seen wearing moonstones at throat and wrist and finger by Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Cressen\" title=\"Cressen\">Cressen</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After <a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a>'s profaning of the sept of Dragonstone and the deaths and imprisonment of its defenders from house <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rambton\" title=\"House Rambton\">Rambton</a>, pious Lord Sunglass declares to Stannis that he no longer supports his claim, which leads to his imprisonment.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Three galleys belonging to House Sunglass—<i><a href=\"/index.php/Piety\" title=\"Piety\">Piety</a></i>, <i><a href=\"/index.php/Prayer\" title=\"Prayer\">Prayer</a></i>, and <i><a href=\"/index.php/Devotion\" title=\"Devotion\">Devotion</a></i>—are seized by Stannis for his <a href=\"/index.php/Royal_fleet\" title=\"Royal fleet\">royal fleet</a>. They take part in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Blackwater\" title=\"Battle of the Blackwater\">Battle of the Blackwater</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Sunglass&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>During the Battle of the Blackwater, Melisandre and Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Selyse_Florent\" title=\"Selyse Florent\">Selyse Florent</a> burn the prisoners in Dragonstone's dungeons, including Lord Guncer, as a sacrifice to <a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">R'hllor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> After Guncer is burned, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Sunglass\" title=\"Lord Sunglass\">his brother</a>, the new Lord of Sweetport Sound, flees to <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The gaoler of Dragonstone, <a href=\"/index.php/Lamprey\" title=\"Lamprey\">Lamprey</a>, wears a soiled white doublet with the seven golden stars of House Sunglass embroidered on it.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> It is unknown whether he took it from Lord Guncer or was a former servant of the house. One of the conspirators who helps Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a> smuggle away <a href=\"/index.php/Edric_Storm\" title=\"Edric Storm\">Edric Storm</a> is Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Triston_of_Tally_Hill\" title=\"Triston of Tally Hill\">Triston of Tally Hill</a>, who had been in service to Lord Guncer.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Sunglass_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\">House Sunglass at the end of the third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Sunglass&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Sunglass at the end of the third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The known Sunglasses during the timespan of the events described in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> are:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Lord {<a href=\"/index.php/Guncer_Sunglass\" title=\"Guncer Sunglass\">Guncer Sunglass</a>}, Lord of Sweetport Sound, a pious follower of the Faith. Burned alive under orders of Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Selyse_Florent\" title=\"Selyse Florent\">Selyse Florent</a>.\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Sunglass\" title=\"Lord Sunglass\">Lord Sunglass</a>, his unnamed brother and heir, the new Lord of Sweetport Sound, currently in Volantis.</li></ul></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Household\">Household</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Sunglass&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Household\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Triston_of_Tally_Hill\" title=\"Triston of Tally Hill\">Triston of Tally Hill</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> sworn to Lord Guncer.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Sunglass&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Appendix\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_25\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 25\">Chapter 25</a>, Davos III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Citadel. Heraldry: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/Heraldry/Houses/1/#In%20the%20area%20of%20King&#39;s%20Landing/\">In the area of King's Landing</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"